1. Download the setup script

   $ wget http://osp.googlecode.com/files/OSP-1.0b3_setup.sh


2. Make the setup script executable

   $ chmod +x OSP-1.0b3_setup.sh


3. Run the setup script

   $ ./OSP-1.0b3_setup.sh


For far more detailed installation documentation, including an
explanation of each step in the setup script, visit
http://code.google.com/p/osp/wiki/Installation.
